7, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-07 09:20", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=860302934,45974302,2077]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66883984]kkk_facai[/uid] (2026-03-07 09:16):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:ac:汗]或者反过来，每天从评论里抽取一些高频而有用的问题。提前设置好，另一个账户周期性提问，数字人按时间轴回复。(回复的假象，但是回复的问题是大多数人想知道的)[/quote]<br/>这个有道理 连拖都可以是程序解决 也不用人工去帮提热度了。", "lou": 1142, "content_length": 59, "reply_to": 860302934, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772846413}, {"pid": 860491771, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 56, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-09 10:43", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "降低石油杠杆 120附近短期过热", "lou": 1143, "content_length": 27, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773024188}, {"pid": 860495126, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 57, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-09 11:03", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "目前GJD没动  买卖都没有<br/>暂时看是4050位置自发反抽", "lou": 1144, "content_length": 45, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773025434}, {"pid": 860509661, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 48, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-09 12:56", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "到目前位置 没有加仓的条件<br/>这个条件之前是写过的", "lou": 1145, "content_length": 44, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773032200}, {"pid": 860510419, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 56, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-09 13:04", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "要么快速缩量  要么GJD进场抄底拉起来  要么金融 科技随便哪个大级别板块快速带量反抽 黄线在上<br/>反正现在啥都没出现。只能观察<br/>70%仓位内", "lou": 1146, "content_length": 120, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773032649}, {"pid": 860513378, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 32, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-09 13:34", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "石油个股我换成黄金股了", "lou": 1147, "content_length": 22, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773034474}, {"pid": 860514388, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 12, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-09 13:44", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我对于石油这边判断是 内资怕 不敢冲 大单拖住小单慢慢跑 不是直接死了<br/>石油票接下来脱离期货 然后到A股特有的短期热点高位博弈  属于柚子打法 我就不去了 <br/>化工 煤炭 甲醇那些都是这样。", "lou": 1148, "content_length": 161, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773035076}, {"pid": 860514762, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 63, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-09 13:48", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=860514686,45974302,2125]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65664557]维拉帕米不是米[/uid] (2026-03-09 13:47):[/b]<br/><br/>我估计狼大买的xckj，就差今天的红色搓揉线了[/quote]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202603/09/jmQ2x-7dhhK6ToS8v-1d.jpg[/img]<br/>以后再估计我就打死你", "lou": 1149, "content_length": 61, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202603/09/jmQ2x-7dhhK6ToS8v-1d.jpg", "size": 6, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202603/09", "name": "jmQ2x-7dhhK6ToS8v-1d.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "24"}], "reply_to": 860514686, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773035285}, {"pid": 860515553, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 24, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-09 13:55", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=860515263,45974302,2125]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67108958]得滑不滑[/uid] (2026-03-09 13:52):[/b]<br/><br/>据亲革命卫队的伊朗媒体称，未来8小时内将有“好消息”公布，相关传闻指向美国总统特朗普或将宣布停火，理由是美方不希望国际油价持续走高。截至目前，该消息尚未得到多方证实。<br/>各种小作文[s:ac:偷笑][/quote]<br/>不用信 就差一口气日韩和东南亚就要买油了 川普不可能放过他们的", "lou": 1150, "content_length": 63, "reply_to": 860515263, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773035724}, {"pid": 860516077, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 37, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-09 14:00", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=860515775,45974302,2126]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38881553]Peace Maker[/uid] (2026-03-09 13:57):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大摁之前说一声 求求了[/quote]<br/>嗯 我会偷偷走的 放心", "lou": 1151, "content_length": 23, "reply_to": 860515775, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773036001}, {"pid": 860516707, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 18, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-09 14:05", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=860516579,45974302,2127]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=41301616]橙伊[/uid] (2026-03-09 14:04):[/b]<br/><br/>鱼大，请问现在是不是还要看券商?科技带量过4117才算安全吧？[/quote]<br/>目前金融没动 能站上4105收盘就不错了 要确认是明天的事<br/>今天没有安全一说 我仓位不会增加", "lou": 1152, "content_length": 85, "reply_to": 860516579, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773036356}, {"pid": 860518862, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 45, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-09 14:24", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "到压力位没有金融<br/>我估计尾盘还要拉石油那些东西避险。。。。MD 麻烦", "lou": 1153, "content_length": 62, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773037470}, {"pid": 860521031, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 33, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-09 14:43", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "4105确实站不上。没有GJD没办法 信心不足<br/>今天就这样了 明天看看GJD动不动", "lou": 1154, "content_length": 66, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773038617}, {"pid": 860521576, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 25, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-09 14:47", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=860521277,45974302,2132]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61059514]lang丶[/uid] (2026-03-09 14:45):[/b]<br/><br/>这个我一直在关注的，上上周算力这块就很强，当然主要是华为晟腾细分的，你要记得的话当时狼大也点过<br/>但是中东那边打起来了直接把节奏断了，但是也没A下去很多辨识度一直在横盘<br/>再到上周算力协同，虽然资金主要去做电了，但是算力这块也算反反复复，还有美利云这种先锋队<br/>再到周末的龙虾发酵，今天要不是周末油价这么异常，按照以往量化的尿性来讲，算力特别是龙虾相关的，早盘就该集体封板的<br/>所以这块这两周其实一直有人顶着外围的大debuff在做，也不算稀里糊涂v起来了[/quote]<br/>今天龙虾已经不及预期了 正常今天应该是少5个板以上的<br/>现在顶多算活着。", "lou": 1155, "content_length": 70, "reply_to": 860521277, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773038879}, {"pid": 860521893, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 36, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-09 14:50", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=860521711,45974302,2132]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42330762]heartvoice[/uid] (2026-03-09 14:49):[/b]<br/><br/>之前gjd兜底的时候 每次兜底都看到有人骂干预市场，希望还市场自由。现在不兜了，一个个哭爹喊娘求gjd救命[s:a2:doge][/quote]<br/>只有我坚定支持GJD 他们不喜欢有人管 我喜欢", "lou": 1156, "content_length": 44, "reply_to": 860521711, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773039034}, {"pid": 860522669, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 23, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-09 14:56", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=860522391,45974302,2132]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=37784933]e471167749[/uid] (2026-03-09 14:54):[/b]<br/><br/>AI应用股性一直都不行，最终还是要硬件支撑才行。。[/quote]<br/>跟这个没关系 今天热点 正常柚子和量化都会批量上板的 但是国算那几个大票今天不算强  那些资金也不太敢<br/>但是只要外面稳定 或者明天后天闭会没有GJD砸盘 那这个方向还是没问题的  前提是这两天不要被别的热点抢过去", "lou": 1157, "content_length": 194, "reply_to": 860522391, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773039408}, {"pid": 860528161, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 38, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-09 15:39", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[img]./mon_202603/09/jmQ2x-3btbK1yT3cSyw-5u.jpg[/img]<br/>这种消息能上新闻你们敢信", "lou": 1158, "content_length": 62, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202603/09/jmQ2x-3btbK1yT3cSyw-5u.jpg", "size": 71, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202603/09", "name": "jmQ2x-3btbK1yT3cSyw-5u.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "120"}], "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773041941}, {